agv daily chart as follow up to their positive corporate development awhile backa rising OBV that correspond to a lower highs. A clear divergence?taking the bottomish long VOP bars as reference  the yellow shaded zone traded 557m at vwap 0.027for reference  only 334m shares are in public hands and those before rights are all deep in the water as the stock collapsed from 20 cent region before the entry of Chua Wei Kee their chairman. That is 166% of public float not in Chua and concerted party's hands.Did a round of rights issue at 2.5 cent to capitalise all his loans to company into shares hence emerging as controlling shareholder of the companythe queries to SGX sometime back gave strong hints on a company turnaround and coupled with Chua's background in the industry (refer to history) it seems an increasing probability on the story.a rounding bottom and breakout at 30 will give an immediate target of 3.9 centthough the 6.3 cent high is giving plenty of room for imagination.
